extendedInfo.description: High or Low is an extremely fun and entertaining drinking game to play. Players go around in a circle guessing whether the next card drawn will be higher or lower than the previous card. The number of drinks a player takes carries over to the next person if the card is guessed correctly.Keywords: High, Low, Drinking, Game, College, Party, Fun, Cards
